subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution in Turkey .
Konya , Antalya , Mersin , Kayseri , Ordu , Giresun , Erzurum , Artvin ( Schawaller 1996 ); Isparta , Düzce , Konya , Antalya , Mersin ,
Hatay
, Adıyaman , Şanlıurfa , Tunceli , Trabzon , Gümüşhane , Erzurum , Kars , Muş , Bitlis (
Háva et al . 1998
); Antalya , Gümüşhane , Erzurum , Erzincan , Aksaray , Niğde ( Açar 2008 ).

Remarks. Widely distributed Palaearctic species, known from Europe to Eastern Siberia (Růžička 2015). In Turkey , recorded in all regions except for the Aegean and Marmara Regions. Here reported for the first time from Adana , Ankara , Batman , Eskişehir , Kahramanmaraş , Mardin and Yozgat Provinces.
